column2: ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE JUST TAKEN THE FIRST RUSSIAN DEFENSIVE POSITIONS. ADVANCING FORWARD. OVER.
ALPHA TO PAPA BEAR. SECOND RUSSIAN DEFENSIVE LINE HAS FALLEN. HOOYAH! OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE CAPTURED THE BASE. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA BLACK. ROGER THAT AND GOOD WORK. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
